City View



The park is on a steep hill -- to get there, we took several flights of escalators and stairs up from the nearest subway stop.
As a result, it has good views of the city. The hill in the background is Montjuïc.
Taken Tuesday, September 11, 2001, 11:29:48am.  Original image size: 1600x1200, 989kb
Technical details: Olympus C700UZ, 1/125s @ F5.6, ISO 100, 38mm
